    "long_instructions": "#### Generate a Beat with A.I. \r\nUse this level to have A.I. help you create a new beats.\r\n\r\n- Click the [play AI drums](#clickable=id-left:play_pattern_ai_at_current_location_simple2) block to generate your own beat.  \r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://images.code.org/f107e484c397d0c57a4d5fa3b4c2697c-image-1742674189869.png\" style=\"width: 150px\">\r\n\r\n- Work the AI to see if you can generate beats to match different musical moods like elevator music, intense combat scene in a move, upbeat pop song, etc.\r\n- Press [Run](#clickable=run-button). \r\n\r\n",
